PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 2001-1392 which correct (a) the spelling of the family name of Staff Sergeant William Angus McKinnon, a Non-Commissioned Officer of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police who was thereby appointed to the rank of Inspector, and (b) the reference to his rank at the time of the appointment.
